Source: pg-bikram-sambat
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/LeohangRai/pg_bikram_sambat

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-bikram-sambat
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-bikram-sambat
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Bikram Sambat date type and conversion functions for PostgreSQL PGVERSION
 pg_bikram_sambat provides a custom Bikram Sambat date type for PostgreSQL,
 including conversion functions between Gregorian AD dates and Nepali BS dates.
